      class  ElementWiseMultiplicationLayer
      Elementwise multiplication layer with weights: implements out = activationFn(input .* w + b) where:
      - w is a learnable weight vector of length nOut
      - ".*" is element-wise multiplication
      - b is a bias vector

      Note that the input and output sizes of the element-wise layer are the same for this layer created by jingshu
      class  RepeatVector
